eccsi-sakke-core is a C++ port and restructuring of the above ECCSI-SAKKE
library (originally in C, OpenSSL-based). The ECCSI (RFC 6507) and SAKKE
(RFC 6508, RFC 6509) operations follow the structure of the original work.

The underlying algorithms are defined by IETF standards RFC 6507, RFC 6508,
and RFC 6509. Standard mathematical techniques used in the implementation
are not covered by the above copyrights.
